Chelsea travel to Amsterdam to face Ajax in the Champions League in Wednesday’s early kick off. The Blues are three points behind their hosts, who lead Group H with six points. Before now, there have been no previous competitive meetings between Ajax and Chelsea. Kick off is 5.55pm West African time. Chelsea XI vs. Ajax: Kepa, Azpilicueta, Zouma, Tomori, Hudson-Odoi, Kovacic, Jorginho, Alonso, Willian, Abraham, Mount Ajax XI vs. Chelsea: Onana; Dest, Veltman, Blind, Tagliafico; Martínez, Edson Álvarez; Ziyech, Van der Beek, Promes; Tadic Wednesday, October 23
